   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" mid="48" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>It wouldn't be good to leave any seed of chaos. Track him down if you can, will you? If he has already entered another lord's territory by passing through the canyon, don't chase him anymore. Got that?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2" mid="49" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Why did the runaway Child appear at Grele's house? Was it really for revenge? Could Grele have unfortunately got into some trouble and got dragged away? There's no way I can find out about where Grele is so I should chase after the Child like what Vernicka said.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
