   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="QW_107.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-" mid="50" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Okay, I'll make my way to the </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Broken Goldstone Canyon</FONT><FONT color=#662500> right now.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-quest_check" mid="54" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>A traveller from the <FONT color=#a82424>collapsing world</FONT>… I've been expecting you...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-b" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>You're... </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Lipius</FONT><FONT color=#662500>?! What are you doing here? Are you a </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>duplicate from Lagendia</FONT><FONT color=#662500> too?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-c" mid="57" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>Huhu… I'm the same Lipius that you know but I'm someone else too. I belong to Lagendia as much as I belong to Mistland. Or maybe I don't belong to both of them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-g" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Ah… Here it goes again... No sane person can stand talking to Lipius... I'll just think that he's a special man so he managed to appear here.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-e" mid="61" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Oh…? You're… an elf with a familiar aura... Have we met before?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-f" mid="62" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>Yes, I'm the original one who came here from Lagendia. We could have met somewhere before, or maybe not... I kept walking and wandering in many paths. Now I'm finally beginning to recover the memories I had lost...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-g" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(What? He's the original person from Lagendia? That's strange. Even if he managed to come here through a Dimensional Gap, anyone from Lagendia would be like a phantom here without a physical body. It can't be that he has a dragon's jewel like me too...)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-h" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I should leave the complicated questions aside first and ask him whether he has seen Grele or the runaway Child.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-i" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>A blue-haired boy and a runaway Child... I've seen someone who seemed to be a Child who's on the run but he was alone.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-j" mid="67" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>He seemed to be looking for someone. Though I didn't know what his intentions were, he left the canyon and entered another territory.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-k" mid="68" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(So Grele wasn't dragged into trouble by the runaway Child. I should ask him about Rubinart and Geraint too, just in case he saw them.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-l" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>Hmm… An arrogant-looking golden-haired boy and a young man with red hair and red eyes who look a hundred times more arrogant than the boy?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-m" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius smiles quietly.)</FONT><BR>Well… I may have seen such a curious combination of creatures, or maybe not... But don't be too worried, traveller.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-n" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>They are alive and well. But the poison in this world is not doing them any good.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-n" image="QN_Iris.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-o" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(What? He's saying the same thing as </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Iris</FONT><FONT color=#662500>… that Rubinart and Geraint are alive but the poison is bad for them...!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-p" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>If this goes on, the <FONT color=#a82424>red-haired man</FONT> will be submerged in poison. The <FONT color=#a82424>golden-haired boy</FONT> will do whatever he can… but they went too far and that would have tied them down...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-q" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Have you met Rubinart and Geraint? Have you met Iris too?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-r" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius smiles silently.)</FONT><BR>I've found the answer but I'm still just a traveller. Travellers meet again in their long journey or part their ways.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-2-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-3" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR>So when it's time, you'll meet them on the same path. Until that time comes, all you have to do is to follow your own path...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1832_gold_lifius-3" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_lifius.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1832_gold_lifius-3-" mid="78" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Lipius$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Lipius seems to have nothing to say anymore. Go back to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Vernicka</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2>.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(Report to Vernicka that the runaway Child seems to have crossed the canyon and entered another territory.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>That's good. The other territory will deal with him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
